{"tid":833902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰】日本考慮與美國簽雙邊協議 降農產品入口關稅","createTime":"2018-09-24T00:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T03:16:11.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f5141eaf9999a224bc3816395f2fce1b32c57d49","tid":833902,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T00:29:45.000Z","msg":"【貿易戰】日本考慮與美國簽雙邊協議 降農產品入口關稅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2167089/%E3%80%90%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E3%80%91%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B0%BD%E9%9B%99%E9%82%8A%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%20%E9%99%8D%E8%BE%B2%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%A3%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2167089%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E9%259B%2599%25E9%2582%258A%25E5%258D%2594%25E8%25AD%25B0%2520%25E9%2599%258D%25E8%25BE%25B2%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%2593%2581%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%258F%25A3%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25A8%2585&d=6IMoQAHszAEhGvitxER%2F4EbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=044a06f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2167089/%E3%80%90%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E3%80%91%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B0%BD%E9%9B%99%E9%82%8A%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%20%E9%99%8D%E8%BE%B2%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%A3%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85</a><br />\n<br />\n日本首相安偣晉三本周與美國總統特朗普會面，商討貿易問題。消息指，日本有意與美國達成雙邊貿易協議，減低美國農產品關稅，換取美國不向日本車加徵關稅。<br />\n<br />\n《日本經濟新聞》報道，日本有意改變立場，考慮與美國達成雙邊貿易協議，並降低美國農產品的入口關稅至美國仍在《跨太平洋夥伴關係協定》（TPP）時的水平，以換取美國不向日本進口汽車加徵關稅。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，日本希望參考與歐盟達成自由貿易協議的模式，與美國商討貿易協議。"},{"pid":"d9b68779e134c01a2293418ac265c996243dc30b","tid":833902,"uid":39365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f5141eaf9999a224bc3816395f2fce1b32c57d49","tid":833902,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":